data.description: Home sustained water damage at the beginning of the year and has been under construction most of that time, almost fully renovated down to the studs as a result.  Just recently showing since completion! Custom Scenic multilevel home on 5 acres w/ full BSMT. Zoned AG/residential in Northern Hamilton County. Large completely remodeled MSTR BR suite w/ tub, sep shower, double vanity. Walk-in closet. KITCH has 35 ft countertop w/ beautiful oak cabinets. New mechanicals. Geothermal, new driveway and outbuilding. No HOA. A must see homesteaders dream! New LVP Floors throughout, New Paint, Upstairs and basement were completely renovated down to studs.  Main floor was 90% renovated down to studs.
